descriptionÚformatter_classz-iz --inputFz^Input audio/video file. If omitted, the script checks only the dedicated whisper_input folder.)ÚrequiredÚ defaultÚhelpz-oz--outputz>Output TXT file. If omitted, a default output path is created.)rŽ  r  z--srt-outputz"Optional SRT subtitle output path.z--wav-outputzKOptional intermediate WAV path. If omitted, a unique cache path is created.z--input-folderz=Optional dedicated folder used for safe input auto-detection.z--device)r   r™   r’   zExecution device.)Ú choicesrŽ  r  z--compute-typezSCTranslate2 compute type, for example auto, int8, float16, float32 or int8_float16.z --modelzIModel name or local model directory. Use auto for CPU/GPU-aware defaults.z
